		{"id":"350a81da587c25fb","type":"text","text":"You're currently using the browser's built-in `SpeechSynthesis` API, which varies wildly by device — decent on iOS (Siri voices), mediocre on Android/desktop Chrome.\n\nFor a web demo, here are better free/cheap options:\n\n**Free & no API key:**\n\n- **Google Translate TTS** — `https://translate.google.com/translate_tts?ie=UTF-8&tl=vi&client=tw-ob&q=...` — Good Vietnamese quality, but unofficial/rate-limited. Many language apps use this.\n\n**Free tier / cheap API:**\n\n- **Google Cloud TTS** — WaveNet voices for Vietnamese (`vi-VN-Wavenet-A/B/C/D`) are very natural. 1M free characters/month. Requires API key.\n- **Microsoft Azure TTS** — `vi-VN-HoaiMyNeural` (female) and `vi-VN-NamMinhNeural` (male) are excellent. 500K free characters/month.\n- **ElevenLabs** — Great quality but limited Vietnamese support and free tier is small.\n\n**Recommendation for a web demo:** The Google Translate TTS endpoint is the quickest upgrade — no API key, sounds much better than browser TTS, and works cross-browser. You'd proxy it through your Express server to avoid CORS issues.","x":-519,"y":-61,"width":438,"height":341},
		{"id":"9a272cd461ac22fb","type":"text","text":"\n| Database                   | Sub-data                                                               | Size       | Words |\n| -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------- | ----- |\n| 🇬🇧  vn_en_dictionary.db  | VE, AI_Generated_EN, Wiktionary, FVDP, **VietAnh_Stardict** (VI→EN)    | **100 MB** | 447K  |\n| 🇨🇳 vn_zh_dictionary.db   | HanViet, AI_Generated_ZH, **TrungViet** (ZH→VI), **VietHan** (VI→Sino) | **76 MB**  | 257K  |\n| 🇯🇵 `vn_ja_dictionary.db` | NhatViet (JA→VI), **VietNhat** (VI→JA)                                 | **54 MB**  | 194K  |\n| 🇫🇷 `vn_fr_dictionary.db` | PhapViet (FR→VI), VietPhap (VI→FR)                                     | **18 MB**  | 86K   |\n| 🇷🇺 `vn_ru_dictionary.db` | DucViet (DE→VI), VietDuc (VI→DE)                                       | **16 MB**  | 74K   |\n| 🇩🇪 `vn_de_dictionary.db` | NgaViet (RU→VI), VietNga (VI→RU)                                       | **15 MB**  | 54K   |\n| 🇳🇴 `vn_no_dictionary.db` | **TBNViet** (ES→VI), **VietTBN** (VI→ES)                               | **12 MB**  | 17K   |\n| 🇪🇸 `vn_es_dictionary.db` | NauyViet (NO→VI) — no reverse available                                | **9 MB**   | 41K   |\n|                            |                                                                        |            |       |\n","x":-1200,"y":311,"width":940,"height":400}
